<p><strong>Copies or transcriptions</strong> of these obituaries are offered at a basic rate of $5 each. To order, please fill out the form on this page or fill out our <a href="http://www.beta.gazettejournal.net/forms/ddb_mailform.html" target="_blank">printable form</a> and send via U.S. Postal Service to Gazette-Journal, P.O. Box 2060, Gloucester, Va. 23061. Please allow six weeks to fill your order.</p>
